'''卡尔史托斯'''（{{lang-de|Karl Storz SE & Co. KG}}）是一家[[德国|德国]][[医疗器械|医疗器械]]公司，主要生产[[内窥镜|内窥镜]]，应用于人类[[医学|医学]]、[[动物医学|动物医学]]，以及[[工业|工业]]领域。

==历史==
1945年成立于[[德国|德国]][[图特林根|图特林根]]，是一家家族企业。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nezhat|first1=Camran|title=Chapter 19. 1960's|url=http://laparoscopy.blogs.com/endoscopyhistory/chapter_19/index.html|website=Nezhat's History of Endoscopy|publisher=Society of Laparoendoscopic Surgeons|date=2005|accessdate=2020-12-13|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727115326/http://laparoscopy.blogs.com/endoscopyhistory/chapter_19/index.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=Berci1996>{{cite journal|last1=Berci|first1=G|last2=Cuschieri|first2=A|title=Karl Storz, 1911-1996. A remembrance.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_surgical-endoscopy_1996-12_10_12/page/1123|journal=Surgical Endoscopy|date=December 1996|volume=10|issue=12|pages=1123|pmid=8939825|doi=10.1007/s004649900261}}</ref><ref name=Schwabian/>1963年成为最早一批推出[[光导纤维|光导纤维]]传递光束的[[内窥镜|内窥镜]]公司。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Gelijns|first1=Annetine C.|last2=Rosenberg|first2=Nathan|editor1-last=Rosenberg|editor1-first=N|editor2-last=Gelijns|editor2-first=AC|editor3-last=Dawkins|editor3-first=H|title=Sources of Medical Technology: Universities and Industry.|date=1995|publisher=National Academies Press (US)|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK232053/|language=en|chapter=Chapter 4: From the Scalpel to the Scope: Endoscopic Innovations in Gastroenterology, Gynecology, and Surgery|access-date=2020-12-13|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128162601/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK232053/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Leonhard2011>{{cite book|last1=Leonhard|first1=Martin|last2=Irion|first2=Klaus-Martin|title=Springer handbook of Medical Technology |date=2011|publisher=Springer|location=Berlin|isbn=978-3-540-74657-7|pages=379–403|chapter=Endoscopy}}</ref>{{rp|382}}<ref name=Lautemann2014/>{{rp|3274–75}}<ref name=Berci1996/><ref name=Lautemann2014>{{cite book |last1=Lautemann |first1=Kerstin |last2=Leonhard |first2=Martin |last3=Stern |first3=Regina |last4=Heda |first4=Jennifer |editor1-last=Doral|editor1-first=M.N.|editor2-last=Karlsson|editor2-first=J.|title=Sports Injuries: Prevention, Diagnosis, Treatment and Rehabilitation|date=2014|publisher=Springer Berlin|location=Berlin|isbn=978-3-642-36568-3|pages=3273–3291|edition=2nd|chapter=Chapter 264: Instrumentation for Arthroscopy and Sports Medicine}}</ref>{{rp|3275}}。2012年全球拥有5,800名员工，年销售额10亿欧元。<ref name=Schwabian>{{cite news|last1=Möllers|first1=Ludger|title=Karl Storz: Schwäbischer Pionier und Firmengründer|url=http://www.schwaebische.de/region_artikel,-Karl-Storz-Schwaebischer-Pionier-und-Firmengruender-_arid,5361524_toid,705.html|work=Schwäbische.de|date=9 December 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706113700/http://www.schwaebische.de/region_artikel,-Karl-Storz-Schwaebischer-Pionier-und-Firmengruender-_arid,5361524_toid,705.html|archivedate=2015-07-06|language=de|accessdate=2020-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1971年成立美国子公司，<ref>{{cite web|title=Karl Storz Endoscopy-America, Inc.: Private Company Information|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapid=4286735|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=23 October 2017|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727145833/https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapid=4286735|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Careless|first1=James|title=Today’s Cutting-Edge Borescopes: A Sampling of What’s Available|journal=Aviation Maintenance|date=June–July 2015|url=https://www.avm-mag.com/wp-content/mag/PDFs/AVM-2015-06-DIGITAL.pdf|access-date=2020-12-13|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023063919/https://www.avm-mag.com/wp-content/mag/PDFs/AVM-2015-06-DIGITAL.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2006年2月在[[上海|上海]][[浦东新区|浦东新区]]成立中国子公司，2020年12月9日在[[上海|上海]][[张江高科技园区|张江高科技园区]]成立中国区总部。<ref>[http://k.sina.com.cn/article_5044281310_12ca99fde02001g5kd.html 德国卡尔史托斯公司中国总部落沪 浦东已有359家跨国公司地区总部]，新浪财经。</ref>

